{"type":null,"faqId":9699,"title":"荣耀畅玩版（g750-t01） WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击</span><span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> <span>&gt; <b>WLAN</b></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，再点击菜单键<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30209\" /></span><span><span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">并进入<b>高级</b></span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span><span>WLAN</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，设置为“始终”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\n\t<span><span><span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30210\" />&nbsp; </span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span><span>3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个选项的含义如下：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">始终：一直保持</span><span><span>WLAN</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">仅限充电时：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span><span>5</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从不（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span><span>5</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"313","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396315750000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":491,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null